items.name: Aardman Animations Style
items.description:
Aardman Animations is a British animation studio known for its stop-motion clay animation techniques and charming storytelling. Founded in 1972 by Peter Lord and David Sproxton, Aardman has become internationally recognized for its unique style and memorable characters.

Aardman's animations are characterized by their meticulous craftsmanship, attention to detail, and a distinct sense of humor. They have produced several beloved and iconic animated works, including the Academy Award-winning Wallace and Gromit series, featuring the witty inventor Wallace and his loyal dog Gromit. Other notable creations include the mischievous Shaun the Sheep, the adventurous Chicken Run, and the prehistoric comedy series Early Man.

The studio's stop-motion animation process involves meticulously crafting characters and sets out of clay or other materials, and then capturing a series of individual frames, slightly adjusting the characters and props between each frame. When the frames are played back in sequence, the illusion of movement is created. Aardman's animations are known for their smooth and expressive animation, as well as the attention to detail in their characters' facial expressions and movements.

Aardman's storytelling often combines humor, heart, and clever writing, appealing to both children and adults. Their animations often incorporate puns, visual gags, and clever wordplay, creating an enjoyable viewing experience for audiences of all ages.

Beyond their films and TV shows, Aardman has also worked on commercials, music videos, and interactive projects. Their distinctive animation style and storytelling techniques have made them a respected and influential force in the world of animation.

Aardman Animations' commitment to craftsmanship, storytelling, and their signature stop-motion animation techniques have endeared them to audiences worldwide. Their endearing characters and whimsical stories continue to entertain and delight viewers, making Aardman a beloved and iconic name in the animation industry.

items.name: Katheryne (Genshin Impact NPC) キャサリン・凯瑟琳 (原神)
items.description:
Made from 32 screenshots of her 3d model (3 processed through IMG2IMG to make the face nicer) and 19 images made using an older version of this LoRA and various checkpoint models, to try and offset the 3d model look. Not happy with the result, but I'm busy, so I dunno if I'll try redoing it later or not.

参考データは3dモデルのスクショ32枚（顔を綺麗にするため、3枚はIMG2IMGで処理した）と、3dモデルのスタイルから離れるために、このLoRAの古い版といろんな別スタイルで作った19枚の絵でした。この結果に満足してないけど、忙しいからいつかやり直すかわかりません。

Recommended prompts （おすすめタグ）:

short hair, medium hair, jewelry, gem, green and white dress, off-shoulder, bow, white pantyhose, vertical-striped pantyhose, puffy sleeves, blunt bangs, detached collar, maid headdress, red bow, green collar, green shoes, corset, blue eyes, black hair

Recommended weight （おすすめウエイト）:

0.7-1.0

Even at these weights, the details tend to be slightly off depending on the checkpoint model used. You'll also need to use the recommended prompts.

このウエイトでも、使ってるチェックポイントモデルによって詳細がよく少しずれてます。おすすめタグも使う必要です。

From my experience, LoRAs seem to work by overwriting what the AI originally intended to draw, based on your prompts. So the more complex a character is, the more you'll need to explain the character's basic appearance. For example, if the AI intended to draw a tight swimsuit, and your LoRA is a big dress, it'll probably make a swimsuit that looks like your LoRA dress (ie. with the skirt missing).

今までの個人体験ですが、LoRAは使ってるタグによってAIが元々描くつもりのキャラクタを書き換えてるっぽいです。ということは、キャラのデザインがもっと複雑場合、その外見の基本をもっとはっきり説明する必要だと思います。例：元々キツイ水着を描くつもりで、使ってるLoRAは大きなドレス。結果は多分LoRAのドレスに似てる水着（スカートなし）の絵になります。

Problems (問題点):

  • Patterns and minor details are often slightly off.

    パターンと細かい詳細がよく少しずれてます。

  • At 0.8-1.0 the style of the face will be less influenced by the checkpoint model.

    0.8-1.0の場合、顔にチェックポイントモデルからの影響が減ります。

Models used for screenshots （スクショに使ったモデル）:

  • Counterfeit v3.0

  • Based65 Final Mix

  • Tsubaki v1.0

  • CardosAnime v1.0

  • ExpMixLine v2

  • Meina Mix v9

  • SweetMix v1.6/1.7

  • CoffeeMix v2.0

  • Anything v4.5 (with Hoyo Artstyle LoRA v2)

主体轻量模型：XSArchi_1***V1，V1将作为主体轻量模型编号进行规整命名，在工作流中起到主导图像生成的工作，复合功能将决定于轻量模型功能。使用权重在0.5-1.3左右。

辅助轻量模型：XSArchi_1***V1.1，V1.1（即此Lora第二版）将作为辅助轻量模型编号进行规整命名，在工作流中起到辅助图像生成的工作，无复合功能，分为视角、风格、应用场景等20余种功能轻量模型，详细功能将在轻量模型介绍中标出。使用权重在0.1-0.5左右。

V2+轻量模型将被更新或迭代。

新轻量模型将分为两种不同的训练、融合、提取等方式进行制作，在库编号相同但版本不同的轻量模型，在训练集的处理上大致无异。在库编号不同但版本相同的轻量模型，功能不同外，训练集及训练方式也各不相同。

新版本将加入中英文命名的方式，解决大家对于模型标识、分类出现的困难。

其余版本介绍：

在库编号100-的轻量模型为早期试用模型，将被迭代。

在库编号100+的轻量模型为正式模型，分为商用及非商用模型，将会持续更新。

在库编号百位数以复数形式出现的为独立授权模型，针对不同平台、企业、组织、个人等进行授权、商用、非商用流通。

在库含有编号的轻量模型被认作为垂类模型库在库模型，将配合XS工作流进行使用。

XS Lightweight model series in the library number 100+ lightweight model will have a new workflow and use methods, roughly divided into the principal lightweight model and auxiliary lightweight model (LoRa, Loha, TI, VAE, etc.).

Body lightweight model: XSArchi_1***V1, V1 will be structured and named as the body lightweight model number, and play a leading role in image generation in workflow. Composite function will be determined by the function of the lightweight model. The right to use weight is around 0.5-1.3.

Auxiliary lightweight model: XSArchi_1***V1.1, V1.1 (i.e., the second version of Lora) will be structured and named as the auxiliary lightweight model number, and play an auxiliary role in image generation in workflow. There is no compound function, and it is divided into more than 20 functional lightweight models such as perspective, style and application scene. The right to use is about 0.1 to 0.5.

V2+ lightweight model will be updated or iterated.

The new lightweight model will be divided into two different ways of training, fusion, extraction and so on. The lightweight model with the same library number but different versions will be roughly the same in the processing of the training set. In addition to the different functions of lightweight models with different library numbers but the same version, the training sets and training methods are also different.

The new version will add the way of naming in Chinese and English to solve the difficulties of model identification and classification.

Introduction to other versions:

The lightweight model in library number 100- is an early trial model that will be iterated.

The lightweight models in the library number 100+ are official models, divided into commercial and non-commercial models, and will be updated continuously.

The number of hundreds in the database appears in the plural form as an independent authorization model, which carries out authorization, commercial and non-commercial circulation for different platforms, enterprises, organizations, individuals, etc.

The numbered lightweight models in the library are considered as vertical model models and will be used in conjunction with the XS workflow.

items.name: Cozy Nest
items.description:
Cozy Nest is a UI extension for Automatic's sd-webui.

https://github.com/Nevysha/Cozy-Nest

Installation

Go in the extenstion tab and search for "Cozy-Nest" or install manually by following those step :

  1. Open your SD-Webui

  2. Go to Extension Tab

  3. add Extenion by pasting this URL, since this extension is not public in the repository, yet https://github.com/Nevysha/Cozy-Nest

Features

  • Fully integrated Image Browser IN BETA. Lots of bugs and missing features. Please be kind with Github issues.

    • Send to txt2img / img2img / …

    • Update with newly generated image

    • Drag and drop image

  • Resizable panels

  • Full Screen Inpainting

  • Customizable tab menu position (top, left, centered)

  • Cozy look with dark or light theme (add ?__theme=light in url or set --theme=light in Auto1111 start arguments to switch to light theme)

  • Bypass Cozy Nest by adding CozyNest=No in URL param (ie: http://localhost:8501/?CozyNest=No) - useful for mobile

  • Save resize bar position / panel ratio in local storage

  • Customize accent color

  • Add or remove accent to the generate buttons

  • Customize font size

  • Move settings in a dedicated collapsible and movable tab

  • Smaller bottom padding bar to get a bit more screen space

  • Setting to center the top menu tabs

  • Setting to remove the gap between checkpoint and other quicksetting

  • Setting to center quicksetting

  • Loading screen with estimated percentage based on previous loading time

  • make settings tab movable

  • Extra network in a dedicated tab:

    • Resizable side panel

    • Customizable card size

  • Drag and Drop tab button inside or outside a “tab container” to bring them or move them from/out main menu

  • Extra Networks left sided tab.

  • Close Extra Network tab with escape key

  • Fetch version from a desicated json file hosted directly in the repo to an easier view of update of Cozy Nest.

items.description:
V3 and V4: Since the special painting method of this artist, if you want to drawing a younger character, you have to add the prompt: chibi .

The artist seems to be very supportive of AI:

Her words in English:

"Seeing AI replacing some of the lower-end painting methods, I feel so satisfied and super excited. There is a feeling that finally some people will have a sense of crisis and take the responsibility for their lack of progress. If you don't have your own unique things or keep up without changes, you will definitely be replaced. Definitely."

"Very practical.

If you are truly in a poverty family and have no time to improve your skills, and this situation is unlikely to change in the long term, I really don't understand why you would choose to enter the art industry, which relies heavily on personal talent more than any other assembly line industry...There is a space for people like you in this industry is because of a shortage of low-level labour. However, these low-level workers are always the easiest to be replaced and are the most unstable group, even without any involvement from AI. I really don't know if it's due to be trapped in an filter bubble or some other reason that so many people have been deceived into thinking they should start with meaningless repetitive work at the bottom.

And even if it's just a beginner, it still requires some time and energy investment. Is someone kidnapping you and forcing you to start learning how to draw from scratch at your desk? If you can afford this initial cost, it probably means that your family is not really struggling financially. But if you are really in this swamp because of poverty, then I strongly suggest that you quit as soon as possible. Without several years or even decades of accumulation, you will always be in the elimination circle. This is not a stable job, there are many other jobs that are more stable than this..."

The contrast of V2 is better than V1.

There are too many names used by this artist, and her ID on twitter is "rei_17" now. If you know she has another names, you can leave it in the comment.

The lightweight models in the library number 100+ are official models, divided into commercial and non-commercial models, and will be updated continuously.

The number of hundreds in the database appears in the plural form as an independent authorization model, which carries out authorization, commercial and non-commercial circulation for different platforms, enterprises, organizations, individuals, etc.

Very  simple to use, just use the keywords, i advice to use togheter bottom_view, photo_from_bottom with a weight like 1.3 should work most of the times.

I used double keyword to give more chance to generate from this perspective as in training images.

upskirt it's self explanatory, should be used togheter with the other 2 when you want to see under skirt.

I used 0.5-0.6 weight in the model for these images, when it doesn't work you might force it with an higher weight but you will probably end up with distorted faces, but you can fix that by inpainting them and then for inpaint cut out this model just to draw properly the face.

items.name: Art - James Doane
items.description:
If there was a board for digital art artists, James Doane would be in the top ten. Can classified his art in figurative or portraitist. However, the special characteristic of his art is that he doesnt do the details, smoothness, fine skin to draw the portrait. In fact, James Doane drew everything with large size of brushes, thick colour and loose rough strokes.

What James Doane did, cannot put into the beautiful group, because there is nothing he drew is beautiful. If there must is a word for it, then it would be wonderful. There is no doubt that James Doane is a master in concept art. He is obviously a master in portrait. However, he also is a magician. Many artists can do painterly, but no one can do the way he did. It is James Doane, the one and only, the magician.

Noted that there will never be the AI model can replace the artist. This is merely at scratch on the surface of the original artworks. Please consider go to his website to buy the print. https://doanedrawings.artstation.com/

Dataset at 400x400 attached.

This is long training and strong model with 9600 steps. Suggested weight .4 to .7.

Model used in gen images https://civitai.com/models/21616/neurogen-v11

Kohya_ss config: 50 repeats, 1 batch, 3 epoch, net dim, alpha, conv dim, alpha 16,16, 8,1.

No commercial for the model and its products.

  • 形式格式上借鉴《元素法典》

  • 【Submission requirements & Methods】

    【1】Must be anime picture/model related and include 2.5D.

    【2】It can be used in most models, at least not just a few models.

    【3】Contribute way for direct picture comments section at the bottom of the https://civitai.com/models/62473 release with images can be generated information.

我不希望看到那些拿着一两个tag关键词就说自己的tag并且不允许别人使用这种行为：也不希望某些人拿着“高贵”的AI图去FanBox等平台自诩所谓的“价值连城”，让别人付费才能购买那劣质的AI图。

I don't want to see people who take a word or two and say it's for themselves and no one else to use

I also don't want some people to take "noble" AI graphics to FanBox or other platforms claiming that they are "worth a lot" and make others pay for that inferior AI graphics.

感谢【秋叶甜品店（频道）】让我有了这个想法。之前就有人提出CIVITAI上模型的提示词都是万年不变的（例如向日葵女孩最早在2月就已经出现了，直到5月10日仍有新发布的模型使用这个提示词），于是就有了整理的想法。

Thanks to Akiba Dessert Shop (Channel) for giving me the idea. It was suggested earlier that the CIVITAI model's parameters would remain the same for thousands of years (for example, Sunflower Girl first appeared in February and was still used in new models released as of May 10), so the idea of reorganizing was born.

祝大家玩的开心＜3

Katy M o'Brian. She's been in The Mandolorian, Ant-Man and the Wasp: Quantumania, The Rookie and some other stuff.
